research", and it's in "an escalation process"! It's been several months now. I'm confused 
because I don't see how a company can be legit and yet act like a scam. Furthermore, one time I 
needed to call a local hospital quickly but the 411 service listed only animal hospitals, with 
no way to try again or clarify!				 
